{"tid":1657262,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"眾志前副主席袁嘉蔚獲批入閘","createTime":"2019-10-16T04:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T04:15:25.000Z","uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"848a1148fca74ba519568bffdf2df003ef8876c3","tid":1657262,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"//【Now新聞台】區議會選舉提名期明日結束，香港眾志前副主席袁嘉蔚參選資格獲確認。<br />\n<br />\n袁嘉蔚在社交網站上載通知書，選舉主任確認她參選南區田灣選區的資格，其間未曾向她查詢。同區已報名參選的是尋求連任的陳富明，他報稱獨立。<br />\n<br />\n另外，參選九龍城樂民選區的林正軒亦獲確認參選資格，他提交的政綱寫明「光復香港，時代革命」，選舉主任未曾向他查詢，同區已報名的是現任區議員楊永杰。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366438&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=233e9544\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366438&h=47bb7adf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366438</a>"},{"pid":"cdcb83bc7d8f8ceb2816ef374b8c8ecbc588d68b","tid":1657262,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a03eb2ce34b294c0f1301fbae6ae82beb6d203c1","tid":1657262,"uid":57674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"邊個DQ邊個做制裁第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470c49057ba1f2df1ba11a7bee8a41211fb76fb0","tid":1657262,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:15:25.000Z","msg":"理得邊個入到閘，成個選舉DQ"}]}